2. Combine graham crumbs, sugar, and butter; press firmly into the bottom of the pan. Bake 10 minutes; cool.

3. Beat cream cheese on medium-low until creamy, scraping often. Add sugar and beat 2 minutes. Add sour cream, vanilla, flour, and lemon zest.

